(1) tag
    invoke AtomicParsley
      >> AtomicParsley <input-file> --title "abc" --artwork path-to-artwork --year 2018 -o "outputfile"
      >> AtomicParsley <input-file> --title "abc" --TVShowName "abc" --artwork path-to-artwork --year 2018 --TVEpisodeNum 4 --TVSeasonNum 1 --TVEpisode "once upon a time..." -o "outputfile"

(2) rip
    ignore already ripped files (MP4 video, MP3 audio, etc.)
    invoke handbrake

(3) go-cli/pipeline
    add support for non-blocking parallel pipeline using buffered channels for concurrent resolving, ripping, and tagging

(4) add dedicated input file for omdb keys